{"tid":1414841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(推推佢)每週香港人新嘅嘗試，就亂散播失敗主義","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:26:04.000Z","uid":58434,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d62c24c4c4aa1cf4ceda8d286cfde23836980682","tid":1414841,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路途雖然遙遠，目標仍然清晰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一致</span></span>"},{"pid":"49ec335f053ad4841787338b30ccb331465b620a","tid":1414841,"uid":58434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"f0596bae9aa9a9125b7674dd26968f6e05d26d09","tid":1414841,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">放核彈都唔割呀！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢D咁既post我都出到啦on9<br />\n<br />\n諗下啦<br />\n我地和理非同勇武已經係命運共同體<br />\n就算我地割左，最尾冇左自由既都係我地<br />\n大家已經番唔到轉頭嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力</span></strong><br />\n自由社會就係每個人都有唔同意見<br />\n勇武派有冇真係傷害過普通市民？有冇針對民居？冇呀<br />\n<br />\n由始至終都係D狗先會亂係民居出彈，射街坊射記者<br />\n佢地而家燒狗屋，唔係對準政權係乜野？<br />\n係呀冇錯佢地有無意中搞到其他紀律部隊，但係都唔夠黑警同黑社會與民為敵咁仆街！！"},{"pid":"a3eadf6c3ef59d4b4340f20760e0e3959eec21b9","tid":1414841,"uid":58434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:53:38.000Z","msg":"對抗不公義"},{"pid":"c6d8bb01dda6d7a527fb1f4e6f5cb6024fee7a79","tid":1414841,"uid":58434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"放下文武成見"},{"pid":"15b479cb66edc310707a1509bac60658e240a3f6","tid":1414841,"uid":58434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:55:13.000Z","msg":"對抗不公義<br />\n放下文武成見"},{"pid":"4ca0385ecdca47fc31f14bd67b209a3852ff594c","tid":1414841,"